{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'The tactical terminal has been activated.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'There was a 0.03-second flicker just above the terminal, but it disappeared immediately...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'No response from the terminal, Lee?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'The tactical terminal well functions and no anomalies were detected.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'No response from the Corrupted detected!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'But I sense a real and murderous feeling all over my body...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Where would the enemies be...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Wait, I figured it out.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'The murderous feeling is gone. What did you do, Lee?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'I closed the tactical terminal for now. Turns out the memory intends to attack us.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "But she won't be able to touch us for real... right?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'The murderous feeling was so real, like a cut on the skin.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "It's hard to imagine that such a feeling comes from a memory.", 4: '1'}
{1: '996', 2: "Seems like it's a powerful one.", 3: '45', 4: "But it shouldn't be able to affect us.", 5: '46'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "In this case, there's no way to properly test the memory. Things are getting a bit tricky.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "In this case, there's no way to properly test the memory. Things are getting a bit tricky.", 4: '1'}
{2: "Perhaps I've got an idea.", 3: '48', 4: 'Lee, reactivate the terminal.', 5: '48'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Commandant, do you have any idea?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Cottie', 3: "Well, what's going on? I'm right in a dream of donuts!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "You won't get away with it if you're waking me up just for some boring little stuff!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "Well, what's this feeling...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "I see. Huh, it was the commandant's idea, right? You've found the right person this time.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: 'Aife, is that you?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Aife', 3: "Cottie... it's been a while.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Cottie', 3: "You're still the same as before, ready to attack others at any time, you cross sniper.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Aife', 3: "Isn't it normal to be on alert and take a defensive stance with weapons at all times?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Cottie', 3: 'Are you calling sniping defense? Forget it, take a good look at the person behind.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Cottie', 3: 'See? These are not your enemies.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Aife', 3: "I knew it. Our battles... won't just end up like this.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Cottie', 3: 'Hmph, after all, "that guy" has barely won my approval. I could never be wrong about others!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'The timing is just right. Test for memory integrity and corruption completed. Ready for recycling.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Aife', 3: 'Sergeants are always at their disposal. Whatever the order is, consider it done.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Alright, Aife?', 3: '86', 4: 'Start recycling, Lee.', 5: '86'}
{2: 'Aife', 3: "Commandant... I haven't heard of it in a while.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'So, all the memory data recycling is completed.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Cottie', 3: 'Hey! Well... Commandant!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Huh?', 3: '92', 4: "Cottie, what's going on?", 5: '92'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "I don't care if you're the commandant of the former Moe Army, our commandant... anyway, listen to me!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "Heads up! I haven't been waiting for someone... or being excited to see someone...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: '... like having a lot of delicious donuts!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "But! If you dare to wake me up from a sweet dream of donuts, you'd have to take responsibility for it!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "I don't care what enemies you're up against, or what damn Punishing Virus, I just want you to win! Got it?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Understood.', 3: '98', 4: 'Leave it to us.', 5: '98'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "And, I'm not looking forward to those words... you know?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "Wel... Hey, don't you have something to say since I offered my help as a powerful marshal?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Welcome back, Cottie!', 3: '102', 4: 'Ah, welcome back!', 5: '102'}
{2: 'Cottie', 3: "Hmph, good luck. I'll be waiting.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Seems like the commandant has made an incredible pact.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "It's a heavy inheritance.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Be sure to win!', 3: '113', 4: "Let's tough it out together!", 5: '113'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "I'm sure we will, Commandant.", 4: '2'}
